                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "As a swift action, the phantom thief can spend 1 Resolve Point to appear insubstantial, fading into the background. Though not true invisibility, this gives the phantom thief a +2 bonus to Stealth checks for the next 10 minutes (+4 if they haven\u2019t moved for the past round). ",
